project.objective:
Services to enhance the innovation management capacity of SMEs in the macro-region 1 in Romania

The objectives of this proposal are the the following: 
- increase the efficiency and effectiveness of innovation processes of local beneficiaries of SME Instrument and innovative SMEs with significant innovation activities and high potential for internationalization;
- facilitate SME's access to consultancy services for innovation management to address bottlenecks to creating an economic impact; 
- support innovative SME''s to raise the company's profitability and competitiveness on international markets.
